ALSA: hda: cix: use ACPI DMA ranges and SG stream buffers

Consolidate the CIX HDA ACPI DMA hardening into one patch: prefer ACPI DMA ranges, allocate stream bookkeeping from a shared coherent block, and enable ALSA SG DMA buffers.

